      <title>南非燃煤电厂允许违反排放规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-s-embattled-eskom-allowed-to-breach-emission-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非允许由国有Eskom Holdings Soc Ltd.运营的八家燃煤电厂违反排放规则，以帮助现金短缺的公用事业集中资源，以提供稳定的电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-s-embattled-eskom-allowed-to-breach-emission-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 08:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
